self = <binarySearchTree3.DoubleLinkedList object at 0x7f7c168292a0>, val = None

    def remove(self, val):
        """Remove first occurance of val from list."""
        curr = self.head
        while curr:
            if curr.data is val:
                if self._length == 1:

        curr = self.head
        while curr:
